    "causal_summary": "Adapt the sk-git skill's worktree handling from Superset IDE's git worktree model. Superset treats each workspace as an isolated worktree with centralized storage, config-driven lifecycle hooks, and structured init/teardown flows. The current sk-git skill uses a simpler, manual-choice model that lacks these capabilities. This adaptation translates Superset's desktop-app patterns into CLI/AI-skill documentation.",
